prodNameC: "亞斯特" 甲胎兒蛋白放射免疫分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1.    AFP Bridge Coated Tubes: 120 tubes. Each carton box contains 60 tubes packed in a plastic bag.  Each tube is coated with mouse monoclonal antibody to AFP.

2.    AFP Bridge Tracer: 2 vials.  Each vial contains I-125 labeled mouse monoclonal antibody to human AFP.  Maximum radioactivity 424 kBq per vial.  Each vial contains phosphate buffer with bovine, horse, sheep         and mouse serum and sodium azide, <0.1% w/w. 63 ml per vial.

3.    AFP Bridge Calibrators: 6 vials.  The vials contain respectively: 0- 2- 10- 50- 200 and 500 IU (0 - 2.42-12.1- 60.5- 242 and 605 ng) of AFP per ml, (1st IS 72/225) in horse serum with sodium azide, <0.1% w/w.  0.6 ml per vial.

4.    Coated Tube Wash Concentrate: 1 vial. The vial contains an aqueous solution of Triton x-100, 8 ml.  Add the contents of the vial to 1000 ml of distilled or deionized water.

5.    Serotest P: 1 vial.  The vial contains lyophilized human serum with sodium azide, <0.1% w/w, 1 ml after reconstitution.  Reconstitute with 1.0 ml distil
applicantName: 泰歷藥品儀器股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市大同區承德路二段81號15樓
efficacy: 用來檢測人體血清、血漿、羊水檢體中甲胎兒蛋白的含量。
